-- Toyota U.S. May sales up 2.5 percent
-- 
-- Mon Jun 3, 2013 10:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/03/us-toyota-autosales-idUSBRE9520O020130603

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp ( 7203.T ) U.S. May auto sales rose 2.5 percent to 207,952 vehicles, the company said on Monday. 
 Toyota only gave total sales figure in the morning and will report fuller results Monday afternoon. The 2.5 percent rise in Toyota's U.S. auto sales was in line with analysts' expectations. (Editing by  Bernie Woodall ; Editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)